# Installer pages
!define MUI_WELCOMEPAGE_TEXT "This wizard will guide you through the process of updating the XLingPaper configuration files for use with the XMLmind XML Editor version 7.2 or higher.$\r$\n$\r$\n\
You should only use this installer if you have already installed XLingPaper version 2.29.0 or higher.$\r$\n$\r$\n\
Important: if you have customized any publisher style sheets, please be sure to make a backup copy of them before running this installer.  The installer may remove them.$\r$\n$\r$\n\
